<figureCitation id="130F2A575C07FFA348FEFB12FF35FB1B" box="[159,251,1229,1254]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="30.[151,250,1915,1937]" captionTargetBox="[233,1351,231,1851]" captionTargetId="figure@30.[192,1395,193,1894]" captionTargetPageId="30" captionText="FIGURE 4. Anisepyris: aeneus species-group. Head in dorsal profile. A. A. brandiri sp. nov.; B. A. elrosi sp. nov.; C. A. eluredi sp. nov.; D. A. elwingi sp. nov.; E. A. erellonti sp. nov.; F. A. estei sp. nov.; G. A. aeneus Kieffer, 1906; H. A. aurichalceus (Westwood, 1874); I. A. bradleyi (Evans, 1959); J. A. longimerus Santos &amp; Azevedo, 2000; K. A. olivaceus (Evans, 1965); L.A.portoricensis Evans, 1966." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1242271/files/figure.png" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">Figs 4B</figureCitation>
